creator: Neend
descriptionHtml:
Neend App - Meditation, Bedtime stories, Sleep Music

Do you find it difficult to fall asleep or have good quality sleep?
The Neend App is your guide to getting a great sleep experience. You can learn to find an inner balance, practice mindfulness, relax and discover a happier you who is more well-rested and fulfilled.

The Neend App is India’s only free sleep app in your regional language for bedtime stories, relaxing sleep music, and meditation. The Neend App is for anyone who has difficulty in falling asleep, wants good quality sleep, or just wants to feel calm and more relaxed.
With all of our offerings approved by sleep experts, 90% of our users who use our app fall asleep within 15 minutes of using the app. The offerings on the Neend App include yognidra inspired bedtime stories with ASMR, white noise, and relaxing music; guided sleep meditations to help you relax and find your inner balance, and calming sleep music to help you sleep better.
Neend App is free to use and download. There are never any ads and everything on the app is free to use.
Download the Neend App today and have a great sleep experience.

NEEND FEATURES:

BEDTIME STORIES
- Hundreds of calming bedtime stories for grown-ups in your regional language
- Inspired by yog-nidra with calming meditations
- Beautifully narrated with calming music to help you relax

SLEEP MEDITATION
- Meditation for every level of experience and lifestyle
- Guided meditations to help you find your inner balance and peace
- Learn meditation skills and learn to get better sleep
- Breathing exercises to unwind before bed.

SLEEP MUSIC
- Dreamy soundscapes in High-definition quality
- An ever-growing library with sounds of Nature, White Noise, and ASMR curated to help your mind relax
- Soothing sleep sounds from nature to ease anxiety and stress
- Tranquil music to soothe your mind and have a great sleep

QUOTES
- Inspiring positive messages to help you get a boost of positivity
- Easy to share affirmations and quotes that help find balance and focus
- Beautiful Good night messages to help you to go to bed with positive thoughts

What is Neend?
While 1 in 3 people suffer from Insomnia globally, India is the 2nd most sleep-deprived country in the world. Adults on average spend 25% of their day-to-day life sleeping. We, at Neend, want to focus on this 25% of human life and make it better so that we can lead a more enriched and fulfilling life. With our current set of offerings (bedtime stories, sleep music, and sleep meditation), we are touching the lives of millions of people who have placed their faith in us.
So, join us, download the app, and get started on the journey to better sleep with us. Thousands of people who were taking sleeping pills earlier are successfully able to sleep without pills now using Neend app in a couple of weeks itself.
If you have any suggestions, ideas, or concerns please write us at surbhi@neend.app

BEDTIME STORIES

With our current set of offerings (bedtime stories, sleep music, sleep meditation and all natural sleep aid products on shop), we are touching the lives of millions of people who have placed their faith in us.
So, join us, download the app, and get started on the journey to better sleep with us. Thousands of people who were taking sleeping pills earlier are successfully able to sleep without pills now using Neend app in a couple of weeks itself.
